  "description": "A plugin that adds pets to game made by OguzhanUmutlu for PocketMine-MP.",
  "readme_markdown": "<h1>\n<a id=\"user-content-complexpets\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#complexpets\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>ComplexPets<a href=\"https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexPets/blob/main/icon.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexPets/raw/main/icon.png\" height=\"64\" width=\"64\" align=\"left\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n</h1><br>\n<p><b>A plugin that adds pets to game made by OguzhanUmutlu for PocketMine-MP.</b><br>\n<a href=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/p/ComplexPets\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/900de3af2f6401c4fd07e4d9d56d6ea520da0360c4367acae80e8cf0cb4f79cb/68747470733a2f2f706f676769742e706d6d702e696f2f736869656c642e646c2e746f74616c2f436f6d706c657850657473\" alt=\"Poggit\" data-canonical-src=\"https://poggit.pmmp.io/shield.dl.total/ComplexPets\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexPets\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a945aad1fe6f4c2de3110391569ff1466c2e4064e476afdbb7bd308b9d999a34/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f6c6963656e73652f4f67757a68616e556d75746c752f436f6d706c657850657473\" alt=\"License\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexPets\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexPets/stargazers\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/fa6b008030f45d23f8c9475957ab65a539a31cc21105e79cd3e6d4c980488911/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f6769746875622f73746172732f4f67757a68616e556d75746c752f436f6d706c657850657473\" alt=\"Star\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/stars/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexPets\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/uasZzZzH8v\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/ce257494de1dc90e9551e05f321c764c1055ff221f3b6e5122d1711b70be3ccc/68747470733a2f2f696d672e736869656c64732e696f2f646973636f72642f3836313934393439333433313530303831313f636f6c6f723d373338394438266c6162656c3d646973636f7264\" alt=\"Discord\" data-canonical-src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/861949493431500811?color=7389D8&amp;label=discord\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-command\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#command\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Command</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Simply type /pets and summon your favorite animal!</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-features\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#features\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>No database</li>\n<li>Pet riding! <strong>NEW</strong>\n</li>\n<li>Pets can sit</li>\n<li>Custom pet names</li>\n<li>Pet inventories</li>\n<li>Advanced follow AI for pets</li>\n<li>Converting pets to spawn eggs</li>\n<li>Change pet's visibilities</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-issues\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#issues\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Issues</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>You can report bugs by simply clicking <a href=\"https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexPets/issues\">me</a>!</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>\n<a id=\"user-content-support\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#support\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\"></span></a>Support</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>You can help me improving this project by clicking <a href=\"https://github.com/OguzhanUmutlu/ComplexPets/pulls\">me</a>!</li>\n</ul>\n<script defer src=\"https://static.cloudflareinsights.com/beacon.min.js/v8c78df7c7c0f484497ecbca7046644da1771523124516\" integrity=\"sha512-8DS7rgIrAmghBFwoOTujcf6D9rXvH8xm8JQ1Ja01h9QX8EzXldiszufYa4IFfKdLUKTTrnSFXLDkUEOTrZQ8Qg==\" data-cf-beacon='{\"version\":\"2024.11.0\",\"token\":\"508eb1d242ef46b690a0886422106e77\",\"r\":1,\"server_timing\":{\"name\":{\"cfCacheStatus\":true,\"cfEdge\":true,\"cfExtPri\":true,\"cfL4\":true,\"cfOrigin\":true,\"cfSpeedBrain\":true},\"location_startswith\":null}}' crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>",
